{
  "stem": "13469.8",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this press man, he kept on asking me Judith every five minutes, how do you feel about this, how do you feel about that, how do you feel about that?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Judith was able to answer it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they asked me as well, but-- as you can see during the talk, there are one or two times when I get a bit stuck in the throat and maybe a bit emotional.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But generally I'm not a very-- well, that's what I like to think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just am like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't seem to be very emotional.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't seem to have a-- I can't express my feelings very well, but perhaps I do have them, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I do get very upset.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, when this Regina Franks, when we went to her funeral from-- Auschwitz survivor committed suicide, I was very emotionally upset about that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, I've been to funerals and things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yes, I do get upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I-- I suppose I can't express my feelings very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I listened to a program the other day about astronauts when they're in the sky.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're engineers and scientists and they're asked to express their feelings of what they see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all they say is they see a great big land mass and it's green and it's blue and it's yellow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people say, how do you feel?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they say, well, I can see all this here kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they say they're not trained to express feelings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're practical engineers is my excuse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but I'm not saying that we don't have feelings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But maybe we're not taught to express them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'm very bad at words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this is, again, where I never learned the English language properly.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
